hands.

555
00:56:35,650 --> 00:56:37,980
In the hand.

556
00:56:37,980 --> 00:56:40,620
If you are getting cool breeze in the hand.

557
00:56:40,620 --> 00:56:41,620
Good.

558
00:56:41,620 --> 00:56:42,770
Both the hands?

559
00:56:42,770 --> 00:56:44,160
Very good.

560
00:56:44,160 --> 00:56:47,630
Please put down your hands.

561
00:56:47,630 --> 00:56:51,820
Left, left, not right so much.

562
00:56:51,820 --> 00:56:57,660
Right hand is the problem, what’s the problem?

