566
00:57:08,860 --> 00:57:09,860
No?

567
00:57:09,860 --> 00:57:15,620
Now you promise Me that you’ll go and write
to him a letter.

568
00:57:15,620 --> 00:57:16,620
Alright?

569
00:57:16,620 --> 00:57:17,620
Just promise.

570
00:57:17,620 --> 00:57:21,760
Put your left hand on here, yes, and now you
promise, put your right hand towards Me.

571
00:57:21,760 --> 00:57:25,840
What are these rings you are wearing?

572
00:57:25,840 --> 00:57:28,560
Better take them out, is better thing.

573
00:57:28,560 --> 00:57:30,410
Is to take them out for the time being.

574
00:57:30,410 --> 00:57:36,340
And also your kala take it out for a while.

575
00:57:36,340 --> 00:57:38,200
Just for five minutes.

576
00:57:38,200 --> 00:57:44,600
You are getting something cool in the hand?

577
00:57:44,600 --> 00:57:47,010
Nothing so far?

578
00:57:47,010 --> 00:57:50,450
This gentleman here, are you getting any cool?

579
00:57:50,450 --> 00:57:54,740
There only, not in the fingers.

580
00:57:54,740 --> 00:58:01,750
It will work out, it will work out.

581
00:58:01,750 --> 00:58:02,920
