644
01:02:31,460 --> 01:02:45,610
(To a child) Yes, come here, come, come, come
to Me.

645
01:02:45,610 --> 01:02:58,050
Let him feel the chakras which is catching.

646
01:02:58,050 --> 01:02:59,050
Are you better now?

647
01:02:59,050 --> 01:03:00,050
Not yet.

648
01:03:00,050 --> 01:03:01,119
Vishuddhi…

649
01:03:01,119 --> 01:03:04,530
Are you alright?

650
01:03:04,530 --> 01:03:05,670
Freddy?

651
01:03:05,670 --> 01:03:07,950
Getting it?

652
01:03:07,950 --> 01:03:09,090
Good.

